  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 1
    m_Localized: 'Fishball fans love the game because its none stop action! '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2
    m_Localized: IShowShark predicted this result last week and nobody listened,
      as usual
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3
    m_Localized: Overtime in any sport is genuinely the most stressful experience
      you can have in the open water
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4
    m_Localized: Sharkbappe really moves like he was built in a lab, absolutely unreal
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5
    m_Localized: Cristiano Reefaldo really woke up and decided to be the craziest
      shark in the ocean every single day
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6
    m_Localized: Nobody is having a better season right now than Lionel Jawsi and
      I will not be hearing otherwise
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7
    m_Localized: Cold take but the Shark Bowl is the greatest sporting event on the
      planet and it is not even close
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8
    m_Localized: Ocean Cup this is year is gonna be crazy with how the Atlanic is
      going fish right now!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9
    m_Localized: Sharkelona going 3:0 against Mancester United. Anyone surprised??
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10
    m_Localized: Sharkbappe really swims like the ocean itself is scared of him,
      most terrifying thing I have ever witnessed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11
    m_Localized: What is Jake Jawl or Logan Jawl that embarssingly lost their boxing
      match the other day? Can never keep them apart?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12
    m_Localized: 'IShowShark is really out there, outswimming professional athlets '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13
    m_Localized: Kevin De Finne sucks, we lost the last match because of him and
      his lazy fins!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14
    m_Localized: Eden Jawzard vs Kevin De Finne whos clears?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15
    m_Localized: 'Lionel Finsi vs Cristiano Reefaldo! Lets settle this debate once
      and for all. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16
    m_Localized: Cant believe there is sharks out there that this the sharkbowel
      is bigger than the oceans cup?!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17
    m_Localized: Romelu Luka-chew really needs to chilllll
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 18
    m_Localized: If I didnt break my fin when I was younger I would be a professional
      right now!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19
    m_Localized: Miss being out in the open water, kicking rocks with my boys!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
